Belle Mitchell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Belle_Mitchell 0 Belle Mitchell (September 24, 1889 – February 12, 1979) was an American film actress. She appeared in over 100 films between 1915 and 1978. She was born in Croswell, Michigan and died in Woodland Hills, Los Angeles.
